 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f52b8405114599fade02d558468d3a92d5094db","tid":1069563,"uid":7468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:10:10.000Z","msg":"我既方法係<br />\n逼佢埋牆角，等佢無得走就攞大毛巾包住佢，再放入貓袋<br />\n去到獸醫度佢見到陌生地方陌生人，就唔敢郁任醫生舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得用醫生姑娘講聲佢驚青，姑娘識處理架喇"},{"pid":"c95c55ce0a784dad119b40d1957fd1386c6649a3","tid":1069563,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"我果隻冇你咁驚<br />\n但都周不時見到人郁就會驚到飛走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係驚到條尾豎哂毛咁走<br />\n但又會跟住人，得閒抱下佢又唔反抗，唔知佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad754cb0b1c20c585dd166b76ae131053200665a","tid":1069563,"uid":165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f52b8405114599fade02d558468d3a92d5094db","tid":1069563,"uid":7468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:10:10.000Z","msg":"我既方法係<br />\n逼佢埋牆角，等佢無得走就攞大毛巾包住佢，再放入貓袋<br />\n去到獸醫度佢見到陌生地方陌生人，就唔敢郁任醫生舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得用醫生姑娘講聲佢驚青，姑娘識處理架喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"已經計劃緊點捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884e702176aca9525da583646dc04985ce8df195","tid":1069563,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"差噉啲嘢 專員幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d737134992264ba3cd7cf7e5b417eaed460fe4","tid":1069563,"uid":215158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"其實多啲陪下佢 等佢放低戒心就自然唔驚你<br />\n利申：屋企隻貓都係咁 依家剩係唔驚我同女朋友"}]}